---
title: Teriyaki Steak with Wasabi Mashed Potatoes & Roasted Broccoli
description: Hankering for a plate of good ol’ steak and potatoes? We’ve got your back. This recipe takes the classics above and beyond with a few flavorful twists. There’s seared steak, creamy wasabi-spiked mashed potatoes, and sesame-sprinkled roasted broccoli. And on top? Sweet teriyaki sauce and fresh ginger create a rich elixir you’ll want to drizzle over everything. And now you can!
